                <a href="/book" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Today</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>About Arrow-Park Ventures</h2>
                <p>Our Mission & Vision</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h3>Empowering Young Leaders Since 2010</h3>
                    <p>Arrow-Park Ventures has been at the forefront of youth development and leadership training. Our comprehensive programs are designed to build character, confidence, and critical thinking skills in young people across the nation.</p>
                    <p>We believe that every young person has the potential to become a leader. Through our carefully structured programs, we provide the tools, mentorship, and experiences necessary to unlock that potential.</p>
                    <ul class="about-features">
                        <li>25+ years of combined experience</li>
                        <li>500+ students trained annually</li>
                        <li>98% satisfaction rate</li>
                        <li>Partner with 25+ schools nationwide</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <div class="about-placeholder">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <circle cx="100" cy="60" r="20"></circle>
                            <path d="M70 90 h60 v60 h-60 z"></path>
                            <circle cx="85" cy="75" r="3"></circle>
                            <circle cx="115" cy="75" r="3"></circle>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <p>Find answers to common questions about our programs</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I book a program for my school?</h3>
                    <p>Simply visit our booking page and fill out the program request form. Our team will contact you within 24 hours to confirm dates and discuss program details.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What age groups do you serve?</h3>
                    <p>We offer programs for students aged 8-18, with specialized curriculum for different age groups and skill levels.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What is included in a program?</h3>
                    <p>Each program includes professional instruction, curriculum materials, team activities, certificates of completion, and leadership development workshops.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Do you offer custom programs?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! We can customize programs to meet your specific school or organization needs. Contact us for a custom quote.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What is your cancellation policy?</h3>
                    <p>We offer full refunds for cancellations made 30 days prior to the program date. Late cancellations have a 50% refund.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Are instructors certified?</h3>
                    <p>All our instructors are certified professionals with extensive experience in youth development and outdoor education.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
                <p>We'd love to hear from you</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-content">
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <form action="/contact" method="POST" class="contact-form-wrapper">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contact-name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contact-email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contact-subject">Subject</label>
                            <input type="text" id="contact-subject" name="subject" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contact-message">Message</label>
                            <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <div class="info-block">
                        <h3>Address</h3>
                        <p>123 Adventure Way<br>Nature Valley, CA 94000</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-block">
                        <h3>Phone</h3>
                        <p><a href="tel:+1-555-123-4567">+1 (555) 123-4567</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-block">
                        <h3>Email</h3>
                        <p><a href="mailto:info@arrowparkventures.com">info@arrowparkventures.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-block">
                        <h3>Office Hours</h3>
                        <p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM<br>Saturday: 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

